{"about_the_game":"<strong>Wizard Cats</strong> is an action roguelite set in a fantasy world where woodland creatures have been imbued with magic to become master wizards. Collect runes and create new spells as you fight through countless unique worlds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover Spells</h2>Craft your own spells by combining the runes you collect. Each rune holds a fragment of magical language, and when combined they form unique spells that reflect the meaning of the words they represent. Experiment with different combinations to discover a limitless array of spells to conquer your enemies. But beware\u2014some spells are volatile and might backfire if you\u2019re not careful!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/spellgen.gif?t=1738886138\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore Worlds</h2>Venture through whimsical landscapes, from enchanted forests to mystical ruins to regular old farms. In each, the actual environment reflects the narrative\u2014perhaps you will be in a forest where there are two warring clans of woodland critters, or you will enter a desert where there are frogs guarding a mystical oasis.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/extras/explore.gif?t=1738886138\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738886138","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738886138","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/dacf3b4161a3dabb4122131057c12db872f3be3a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738886138","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176500/dacf3b4161a3dabb4122131057c12db872f3be3a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738886138","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"cont